    dc:description "FIGURES 9–14. Male genitalia, a. clasping apparatus, b. phallus. 9. Karschiola ndzou sp. n., HT, LG 6065 (ANHRT). 10. Idem, PT, LG 6123 (ANHRT). 11. Idem, LG 6124 (ANHRT). 12. K. holoclera, AV 6315 (ANHRT). 13. Idem, LG 6122 (ANHRT). 14. Idem, LG 6118 (MWW)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10184176/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10184178>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–20. Male genitalia, details of uncus. 15. Karschiola ndzou sp. n., HT, LG 6065 (ANHRT). 16. Idem, PT, LG 6123 (ANHRT). 17. Idem, LG 6124 (ANHRT). 18. K. holoclera, AV 6315 (ANHRT). 19. Idem, LG 6118 (MWW). 20. Idem, LG 6122 (ANHRT)." ;
