<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10184182>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21–24. Female genitalia. 21. Karschiola ndzou sp. n., paratype, LG 6066 (ANHRT). 22. Idem, paratype, LG 6240 (ANHRT). 23. K. holoclera, LG 6120 (MWW). 24. Idem, AV 6316 (ANHRT)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10184182/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10184184>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25–26. Female genitalia: ovipositor, pheromone gland (pg) and postvaginal plate (pvp). 25. Karschiola ndzou sp. n., paratype, LG 6240 (ANHRT). 26. K. holoclera, LG 6120 (MWW)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10184184/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

